        <div class="section">
          <h2>Version History</h2>
{{VERSION_HISTORY}}
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <h2>Installation Instructions</h2>
          <div class="instructions">
            <div class="instruction-card">
              <h4>macOS</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Download the <code>.dmg</code> file appropriate for your Mac:</li>
                <li><strong>Apple Silicon</strong> (M1/M2/M3): Use the <code>arm64</code> version</li>
                <li><strong>Intel</strong>: Use the <code>x86_64</code> version</li>
                <li>Open the <code>.dmg</code> file and drag Barqly Vault to Applications</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="instruction-card">
              <h4>Windows</h4>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Installer (Recommended)</strong>: Download the <code>.msi</code> file and run it</li>
                <li><strong>Portable</strong>: Download the <code>.zip</code> file, extract, and run the executable</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="instruction-card">
              <h4>Linux</h4>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>AppImage (Universal)</strong>: Download, make executable (<code>chmod +x</code>), and run</li>
                <li><strong>Debian/Ubuntu</strong>: Download the <code>.deb</code> file and install with <code>dpkg -i</code></li>
                <li><strong>RedHat/Fedora</strong>: Download the <code>.rpm</code> file and install with <code>rpm -i</code></li>
                <li><strong>Standalone</strong>: Download the <code>.tar.gz</code> file and extract</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p style="margin-top: 2rem; color: var(--brand-gray); font-size: 0.95rem;">
            <strong>Security Note:</strong> For verification, always check the SHA256 checksums against the <code>checksums.txt</code> file included with each release.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
          <p>
